McKendree University is a nationally ranked, private university offering a variety                   of undergraduate and graduate programs in the St. Louis region, Southern Illinois                   and online. As a Bearcat, you’ll join a vibrant community, make valuable connections,                   and serve others in the world around you. You’ll develop strong leadership skills,                   learn from expert faculty, and attain the personalized education you deserve.

We believe your university experience should be more than just a stepping stone to                   your career. Our close-knit campus community gives you endless opportunities to grow                   as a person, and our long list of scholarships and financial aid programs makes college                   affordable for everyone. Enjoy one-on-one relationships with professors who are passionate                   about what they teach. Meet lifelong friends in our many student clubs, sports teams,                   and exciting campus activities. Make your voice heard at a university that’s dedicated                   to empowering you for success.
